## 1. 현재 (2026) AI/ML drug discovery landscape

### 1.1 Structure prediction (foundation layer)
- **AlphaFold 3** (DeepMind, 2024 Nobel Chemistry) — protein–ligand–DNA–RNA complex 예측
- **OpenFold / ESMFold** (Meta) — open AlphaFold variants, ESM-2 LLM 기반
- **Boltz-1** (MIT, 2024) — open-source AF3-class quality
- **Chai-1** (Chai Discovery) — AF3-class, 상업 친화 라이선스
- **RoseTTAFold All-Atom** (Baker lab) — small molecule + protein 통합

### 1.2 Generative design (de novo layer)
- **RFdiffusion** (Baker) — de novo protein backbone diffusion
- **ProteinMPNN** (Baker) — sequence design (inverse folding)
- **FrameDiff / FrameFlow** — backbone diffusion variant
- **Genie / Chroma** — generative protein model
- **DiffDock** (MIT) — generative ligand docking

### 1.3 Industrial AI biotech
- **Insilico Medicine Pharma.AI** — ISM001-055 (TNIK inhibitor) IPF/ALS Phase 2 진행
- **Recursion + Exscientia** (2024 합병) — phenomics + AI design
- **BenevolentAI** — knowledge graph + LLM
- **Atomwise / XtalPi / Schrödinger** — computational hit-finding
- **Cradle.bio + Generate Biomedicines** — AI antibody / protein design
- **Isomorphic Labs** (DeepMind spinout) — AlphaFold drug discovery 본격화

### 1.4 LLM agent layer
- **Anthropic Claude (Opus 4.7 / Sonnet 4.5)** — long-context literature reasoning
- **OpenAI GPT-4o / o1 / o3** — chain-of-thought scientific reasoning
- **Google Gemini 2.5 Pro / Ultra** — multimodal (image + sequence + text)
- 공통 한계: hallucination, scientific rigor gap, citation fabrication

